				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/B%E1%BA%AFc-chinh-B%E1%BA%AFc-quy-ch%C3%AD-Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-m%E1%BA%B7c-ch%E1%BA%BF-ph%C3%B3ng-v%C3%A3ng-Phu-Ch%C3%A2u-t%C3%A1c/poem-xRXhuUOmluK39LpCU7hkCA">Bắc chinh - Bắc quy chí Phụng Tường, mặc chế phóng vãng Phu Châu tác - 北征－北歸至鳳翔，墨制放往鄜州作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/C%E1%BB%95-phong-k%E1%BB%B3-10-T%E1%BB%81-h%E1%BB%AFu-th%C3%ADch-th%E1%BA%A3ng-sinh/poem-ozKSy7N1ZRlLRDlp_SSTkQ">Cổ phong kỳ 10 (Tề hữu thích thảng sinh) - 古風其十（齊有倜儻生）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Qu%C3%A2n/D%E1%BB%AF-T%E1%BB%91ng-Nguy%C3%AAn-T%C6%B0-th%C6%B0/poem-Fk7M5o-dqL6AuQPDbATmEQ">Dữ Tống Nguyên Tư thư - 與宋元思書</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Qu%C3%A2n/author-WIhCtLwouoSDlIo0qbk1DA">Ngô Quân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Mi%E1%BB%87n/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-ho%E1%BA%A1-mai/poem-xOogqNjbaXknquxnAP16aQ">Đề hoạ mai - 題畫梅</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Mi%E1%BB%87n/author-fEGcjpEMDS77hLL_7VN-Wg">Vương Miện</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-T%C6%B0-Gi%E1%BA%A3n/%C4%90%E1%BB%91i-v%C5%A9/poem-uRfmONeqJt0WnG7KlsIRLQ">Đối vũ - 對雨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-T%C6%B0-Gi%E1%BA%A3n/author-k2nQ5fnr9ZRE2MDraIsNMQ">Nguyễn Tư Giản</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-D%C6%B0-Ngh%C4%A9a/Giang-Nam-xu%C3%A2n/poem-Oavs0xm1-iONIiBaW7RSsw">Giang Nam xuân - 江南春</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-D%C6%B0-Ngh%C4%A9a/author-_2_KNqIhiUMk8s_AJgW7Nw">Trần Dư Nghĩa</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien